 instructional videos. The videos show you how to tie the sling and help you figure out how to wear your baby in various positions, including cradle, kangaroo, tummy to tummy, and hip.","While the website doesn&#39;t offer specific weight and age guidelines, most of its slings are suitable for babies weighing 8 to 25 pounds, aged from birth through the toddler years. The website only specifies that you can use the sling from birth until your child becomes too heavy for your comfort. If you want a sling that can handle more weight, you might want to consider the <a href=\"/best-baby-wraps\">Moby Wrap</a>, which holds up to 35 pounds.Â "]},"id":"18af0e95-396e-42e1-b990-1e56dfb7af08","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_58778","url":"/sakura-bloom-pure-baby-sling-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"grant-morgan","url":"/author/grant-morgan","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Grant Morgan","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"5h9THR5HH34dskUikqZYj8","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-02-03T23:52:15Z","datePublished":"2014-02-03T23:52:15Z","name":"Sakura Bloom Classic","synopsis":"Sakura Bloom is a company that sells numerous baby sling options. This company offers several collections to help you find the perfect baby sling for you and your child, including Classic, Chambray, Cashmere and Bamboo.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Sakura Bloom is a company that sells numerous baby sling options. This company offers several collections to help you find the perfect baby sling for you and your child, including Classic, Chambray, Cashmere and Bamboo.","language":"en","dateModified":"2014-02-03T23:52:15Z","id":"sH6dK3nxQ43hhFh9WFrWhe","meta":{"title":"Sakura Bloom Pure Baby Sling Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"Sakura Bloom provides numerous options to help you find the perfect baby wrap. Read more about these slings here."},"product